ut%20did%20you%20know%20there%20was%20a%20time%20when%20Mr%20Perry's%20heart%20had%20stopped%20beating%20during%20surgery%3F%20He%20was%2049%20at%20that%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20actor%2C%20in%20his%20memoir%20%26quot%3BFriends%2C%20Lovers%20and%20the%20Big%20Terrible%20Thing%26quot%3B%2C%20spoke%20about%20the%20time%20when%20he%20suffered%20a%20burst%20colon%20due%20to%20drug%20usage%20in%202018.%20It%20also%20required%20multiple%20surgeries%20and%20the%20use%20of%20a%20colostomy%20bag%20for%20months%20after.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20People%2C%20Mr%20Perry%20had%20said%20that%20he%20was%20in%20the%20hospital%20for%20a%20period%20of%20five%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20doctors%20told%20my%20family%20that%20I%20had%20a%20two-percent%20chance%20to%20live.%20That's%20the%20time%20I%20really%20came%20close%20to%20my%20life%20ending%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMr%20Perry%20added%20that%20he%20slipped%20into%20a%20coma%20for%20weeks.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EHe%20also%20recalled%20the%20time%20when%20his%20heart%20stopped%20beating%20for%20five%20minutes%20during%20surgery%2C%20the%20report%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20wasn't%20a%20heart%20attack%20%E2%80%94%20I%20didn't%20flatline%20%E2%80%94%20but%20nothing%20had%20been%20beating%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20had%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20Mr%20Perry%2C%20his%20memoir%20was%20dedicated%20to%20%26quot%3Ball%20of%20the%20sufferers%20out%20there.%26quot%3B%20In%20the%20prologue%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20should%20be%20dead.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698567120000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2F9ruk3dl_matthew-perry_625x300_29_October_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwhen-matthew-perry-s-heart-stopped-beating-for-five-minutes-during-a-burst-colon-surgery-4524450%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22First%20responders%20found%20Matthew%20Perry%20un