0them%20laugh.%20Some%20said%20that%20they%20were%20unable%20to%20believe%20the%20news%2C%20while%20some%20thanked%20him%20for%20making%20their%20lives%20better.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%20%3Cp%3EOne%20user%20wrote%2C%20''Waking%20up%20to%20the%20saddest%20and%20heartbreaking%20news%20of%20the%20day%2C%20who%20will%20take%20care%20of%20Joey%20now.%20Rest%20In%20Peace%20Chandler%20Bing.''%20Another%20commented%2C%20''Yes%20Matty%2C%20you%20will%20be%20missed.%20On%20days%20we%20open%20Netflix%20to%20watch%20%E2%80%9Csomething%20else%E2%80%9D%20and%20still%20end%20up%20watching%20friends%2C%20On%20days%20we%20have%20a%20bad%20day%20and%20need%20a%20friend%2C%20On%20days%20we%20just%20want%20to%20turn%20back%20the%20clock%20%E2%80%98cause%20we%20are%20feeling%20old.''%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20third%20wrote%2C%20''ChandlerBing%20is%20one%20of%20my%20fave%20characters%20of%20all%20time%2C%20the%20sarcastic%20smart%20ass%20who%20made%20us%20all%20laugh!%20He%20will%20be%20so%20missed%20but%20in%20his%20work%20%26amp%3B%20especially%20that%20character%20%26amp%3B%20the%20re-runs%20of%20%23Friends%20his%20work%20will%20be%20revered%20FOREVER!!!''%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20fourth%20added%2C%20''Whether%20he%20was%20Chandler%20Bing%20or%20Matthew%20Perry%2C%20he%20always%20wanted%20to%20make%20us%2C%20the%20audience%2C%20laugh.%20we%20were%20always%20his%20first%20thought.%20and%20for%20that%2C%20i%20will%20always%20love%20you.%20I%20know%20I%20didn't%20know%20you%20personally%2C%20but%20you%20made%20me%20so%20happy.%C2%A0You're%20at%20peace%20now%2C%20Matthew%20Perry.''%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHere%20are%20some%20reactions%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EYes%20Matty%2C%20you%20will%20be%20missed.%3Cbr%3E%20%3Cbr%3E%20On%20days%20we%20open%20Netflix%20to%20watch%20%E2%80%9Csomething%20else%E2%80%9D%20and%20still%20end%20up%20watching%20friends%2C%3Cbr%3E