0Our%20AI%20converts%20the%20temperature%20distribution%20to%20a%20cancer%20screening%20report.%20It%20predicts%20if%20there%20is%20an%20abnormality%20or%20not.%20After%20this%2C%20the%20patients%20can%20go%20for%20an%20ultrasound%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Geetha.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSo%20instead%20of%20100%20people%20going%20for%20an%20invasive%20mammogram%20or%20ultrasound%2C%20only%20the%202%20to%208%20who%20are%20detected%20with%20an%20abnormality%20can%20go%20in%20for%20further%20testing.%20This%20is%20a%20universal%20cancer%20screening%20solution%20and%20is%20globally%20relevant%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F04%2Fcervicheck-screening-kit-1681741153.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221155%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20self-sampling%20kit%20can%20be%20used%20by%20women%20directly%20to%20collect%20their%20own%20samples%20at%20home.%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-315524%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22692%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20self-sampling%20kit%20can%20be%20used%20by%20women%20directly%20to%20collect%20their%20own%20samples%20at%20home.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F315492%2Fvadodara-pragmatech-healthcare-solutions-cervicheck-kits-detect-cervical-cancer-at-home%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ECervicheck%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECervical%20cancer%2C%20if%20detected%20early%20and%20treated%20promptly%2C%20can%20be%20effectively%20cured.%20Typically%2C%20it%20takes%2015%20to%2020%20years%20for%20cervical%20cancer%20to%20develop%20in%20women%20with%20normal%20immune%20systems%2C%20whereas%20for%20women%20with%20compromised%20immune%20systems%2C%20like%20those%20with%20untreated%20HIV%20infection%2C%20the%20development%20time%