ts%2Fnews%2Fsebi-turns-up-heat-on-unregistered-influencers-giving-tips-on-social-media-123102900121_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fmarkets%2Fnews%2Fsebi-turns-up-heat-on-unregistered-influencers-giving-tips-on-social-media-123102900121_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Delhi%20Air%20Quality%20'Very%20Poor'%20Despite%20AAP's%2015-Point%20Action%20Plan%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EDelhi%2C%20Noida%2C%20and%20Gurugram%20are%20in%20the%20grip%20of%20'Very%20Poor'%20to%20'Poor'%20air%20quality%2C%20with%20Air%20Quality%20Index%20(AQI)%20ranging%20from%20221%20to%20341%2C%20sounding%20the%20alarm%20for%20residents%20in%20the%20National%20Capital%20Region%20(NCR).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDespite%20a%2015-point%20winter%20action%20plan%20to%20curb%20the%20rising%20pollution%2C%20the%20battle%20against%20deteriorating%20air%20quality%20continues.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20initiatives%20like%20'Red%20Light%20on%2C%20Gaadi%20off'%20are%20in%20motion%20as%20vehicular%20and%20biomass%20burning%20emissions%20contribute%20to%20rising%20PM2.5%20levels%2C%20the%20haze%20is%20likely%20to%20linger%2C%20with%20'Very%20Poor'%20air%20quality%20forecast%20for%20the%20region%20from%20October%2029%20to%2031%2C%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20overall%20air%20quality%20in%20the%20national%20capital%20on%20Sunday%20was%20recorded%20in%20the%20'Very%20Poor'%20category%2C%20as%20per%20the%20System%20of%20Air%20Quality%20and%20Weather%20Forecasting%20and%20Research%20(SAFAR)-India.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20AQI%20in%20Delhi%20was%20recorded%20at%20309%20on%20Sunday%20morning.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20latest%20data%20from%20SAFAR-India%2C%20the%20air%20quality%20around%20Delhi%20University%20was%20recorded%20at%20341%20(Very%20Poor)%20in%20the%20morning%20hours%20while%20in%20IIT%20area%20it%20was%20recorded%20at%20300.%20Similarly%2C%20in%20Lodhi%20Road%20area%20it%20was%20recorded%20at%20262%20in%20the%20'Poor'%20category.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndia%20Meteorological%20Department%20(IMD)%20in%20its%20bulletin%20on%20Delhi's%20Air%20Quality%20forecasted%20predominant%20surface%20wind%20likely%20from%20variable%20directions%20in%20Delhi%20with%20wind%20speed%2004-08%20kmph%2C%20resulting%20in%20mainly%20clear%20sky%20and%20mist%20in%20the%20morning%20on%20October%2029.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20coming%20under%20the%20'Poor'%20category%2C%20the%20IIT%20Delhi%20region%20recorded%20an%20AQI%20of%20300%20and%20in%20the%20Mathura%20Road%20area%2C%20it%20was%20recorded%20at%20228.%20The%20quality%20of%20air%20at%20the%20Airport%20(T3)%20was%20in%20the%20'Very%20Poor'%20category%2C%20with%20an%20AQI%20of%20323.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Noida%20recorded%20an%20AQI%20of%20317%20(Very%20Poor)%20and%20Gurugram%20221%20(Poor).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEarlier%20on%20Friday%2C%20Delhi%20Environment%20Minister%20Gopal%20Rai%20said%20that%20a%2015-point%20winter%20action%20plan%20is%20being%20implemented%20one%20by%20one%20to%20curb%20the%20pollution.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDelhi%20Chief%20Minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20had%20earlier%20announced%20a%2015-point%20winter%20action%20plan%20to%20curb%20the%20pollution%20caused%20by%20vehicles%2C%20biomass%20burning%2C%20dust%2C%20etc.%20Now%20this%20winter%20action%20plan%20is%20being%20implemented%20on%20the%20ground%20one%20by%20one%20to%20reduce%20the%20pollution%20in%20the%20national%20capital%2C%26quot%3B%20Rai%20told%20ANI.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi%20Minister%20said%20that%20since%20one%20of%20the%20major%20causes%20of%20the%20pollution%20is%20vehicles%2C%20they%20have%20started%20the%20'Red%20Light%20on%2C%20Gaadi%20off'%20campaign%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNow%20the%20data%20says%20that%20in%20AQI%20the%20level%20of%20Particulate%20matter%20(PM)%2010%20is%20decreasing%20and%20that%20of%20PM2.5%20is%20increasing.%20This%20means%20that%20pollution%20caused%20by%20vehicles%20and%20biomass%20burning%20is%20increasing.%20For%20this%2