beth%20Ellington%2C%20a%20real%20estate%20investor.%20This%20story%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20owned%20a%20rental%20property%20in%20Fiji%20and%20have%20been%20renting%20and%20managing%20properties%20ever%20since.%20Now%20I%20rent%20out%20other%20properties%20using%20Vrbo%20and%20Airbnb.%20Although%20I%20use%20both%2C%20they%20have%20different%20strengths.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20currently%20list%20two%20properties%20on%20both%20Airbnb%20and%20Vrbo%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20my%20properties%20is%20called%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3D55d4f1f611cd06a4d86c40e96e6b8248bc55233b750164bc13179c96e265f647%26postID%3D653bfed4d5adb6e8ec7f2183%26postSlug%3Dairbnb-vs-vrbo-heres-host-prefers-2023-10%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.airbnb.com%252Frooms%252F52061526%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EHappy%20Haus%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20a%20second%20one%20is%20called%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3D92fabb06b5ad39c0268eb5683a6ad93d203ced6f380313dabf6e4d1e44f40b7d%26postID%3D653bfed4d5adb6e8ec7f2183%26postSlug%3Dairbnb-vs-vrbo-heres-host-prefers-2023-10%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.airbnb.com%252Frooms%252F49210031%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EGilded%20Nest%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20make%20about%20%2435%2C000%20yearly%20on%20Happy%20Haus%20and%20%2420%2C000%20on%20the%20Gilded%20Nest.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20manage%20them%20myself%20and%20work%20three%20hours%20a%20week.%20It's%20been%20a%20significant%20income%20source%2C%20and%20I%20love%20managing%20the%20properties.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20got%20started%20in%201999%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%201999%2C%20I%20was%20a%20single%20mom%20with%20a%20three-year-old%20daughter%20and%20worked%20as%20a%20travel%20agent.%20I%20took%20a%20trip%20with%20my%20daughter%20to%20Fiji%20and%20fell%20in%20love%20with%20the%20we