ward%20me%2C%20arguing%20that%20the%20media%20itself%20is%20the%20problem.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20guess%20I%20shouldn't%20be%20talking%20to%20you%2C%20then%2C%26quot%3B%20Rep.%20Ken%20Buck%20of%20Colorado%20quipped%2C%20while%20Hawley%20deadpanned%20that%20%26quot%3Byou%20guys%20are%20generally%20a%20very%20negative%20influence.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20guys%20continue%20to%20give%20airtime%20and%20platform%20to%20folks%20like%20that%2C%20don't%20be%20shocked%20then%20that%20that's%20what%20people%20do%2C%26quot%3B%20Rep.%20Mike%20Lawler%20of%20New%20York%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYet%20Republicans%20have%20agency%20in%20all%20of%20this%2C%20and%20what%20has%20happened%20over%20time%20is%20not%20simply%20a%20story%20of%20well-meaning%20people%20responding%20to%20perverse%20incentives%2C%20but%20of%20Republicans%20seeing%20those%20incentives%20and%20consciously%20deciding%20to%20take%20advantage%20of%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey're%20doing%20it%20for%20the%20purposes%20of%20exposure%20and%20money%2C%26quot%3B%20Tillis%20said.%20%26quot%3BIf%20there%20is%20a%20long-term%20goal%20in%20mind%2C%20boy%2C%20I'd%20like%20them%20to%20reveal%20it%20at%20some%20point%2C%20because%20I've%20been%20here%20for%20eight%20and%20a%20half%20years%2C%20and%20I've%20seen%20people%20like%20them%20come%20and%20go.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221999%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Rep.%20Ken%20Buck%20speaks%20to%20reporters%20outside%20the%20Capitol%20on%20May%2031%2C%202023.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F653c18ae0487ff031cb11c5c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERep.%20Ken%20Buck%20speaks%20to%20reporters%20outside%20the%20Capitol%20on%20May%2031%2C%202023.%3Cp%3EWin%20McNamee%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20have%20adapted%20to%20the%20terrain%20better%20than%20others.%20Take%20Sen.%20Ted%20Cruz%20of%20Texas%2C%20for%20ex