%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20Opposition%20leaders%20have%20spoken%20on%20the%20issue%20individually%2C%20the%20Communist%20Party%20of%20India%20(Marxist)-CPI%20have%20issued%20a%20joint%20statement%2C%20calling%20for%20an%20immediate%20ceasefire.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIndia%E2%80%99s%20abstention%20on%20a%20resolution%20that%20was%20overwhelmingly%20adopted%20shows%20the%20extent%20to%20which%20Indian%20foreign%20policy%20is%20being%20shaped%20by%20being%20a%20subordinate%20ally%20of%20US%20imperialism%20and%20the%20Modi%20government%E2%80%99s%20actions%20for%20consolidating%20the%20US-Israel-India%20nexus.%20This%20negates%20India%E2%80%99s%20longstanding%20support%20to%20the%20Palestinian%20cause%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcpim.org%2Fpressbriefs%2Fstop-genocidal-aggression-gaza-cpim-cpi-joint-statement%5C%22%3Eread%20the%20joint%20statement%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20titled%20%E2%80%98Stop%20this%20Genocidal%20Aggression%20in%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20signed%20by%20CPI(M)%20General%20Secretary%20Sitaram%20Yechury%20and%20CPI%20General%20Secretary%20D.%20Raja.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CRespecting%20the%20overwhelming%20mandate%20of%20the%20UN%20General%20Assembly%20there%20must%20be%20an%20immediate%20ceasefire.%20The%20United%20Nations%20must%20re-energize%20itself%20to%20implement%20the%20mandate%20of%20the%20Security%20Council%20for%20a%202-State%20solution%20with%20pre-1967%20borders%20with%20East%20Jerusalem%20as%20the%20capital%20of%20State%20of%20Palestine%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20UN%20resolution%20also%20emphasised%20the%20importance%20of%20adhering%20to%20international%20humanitarian%20law%20and%20urged%20the%20unconditional%20release%20of%20all%20captive%20civilians%20as%20well%20as%20the%20unhindered%20supply%20of%20essential%20provisions%20to%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20UN%20resolution%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FUN_PGA%2Fstatus%2F1717995977758384336%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egarnered%20120%20affirmative%20votes%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20while%20only%2014%20countries%2C%20including%20Israel%2C%20the%20United%20States%2C%20Hungary%20and%20five%20Pacific%20island%20states%2C%20voted%20against.%20India%20was%20among%20the%2045%20countries%20%E2%80%93%20most%20from%20the%20Western%20military%20bloc%20%E2%80%93%20that%20chose%20to%20abstain%20in%20the%20vote%20at%20an%20emergency%20session%20of%20the%20UNGA%20in%20New%20York%20on%20Friday%20afternoon.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698499181000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F28184005%2Fimage-1453.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fshocked-ashamed-opposition-hits-out-at-modi-govt-for-refusing-to-back-un-resolution-for-gaza-ceasefire%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22While%20Opposition%20leaders%20have%20spoken%20on%20the%20issue%20individually%2C%20the%20Communist%20Party%20of%20India%20(Marxist)-CPI%20have%20issued%20a%20joint%20statement%2C%20calling%20for%20an%20immediate%20ceasefire.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fshocked-ashamed-opposition-hits-out-at-modi-govt-for-refusing-to-back-un-resolution-for-gaza-ceasefire%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ericsson%20announces%20setting%20up%206G%20research%20and%20development%20centre%20in%20Chennai%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698498895000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-04%2F05%2Ffull%2F1680716744-8673.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fericsson-announces-setting-up-6g-research-and-development-centre-in-chennai-123102800688_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ericsson's%20rival%20Nokia%20has%20already%20set%20up%20a%206G%20lab%20in%20B