2Fmahua-moitra-cash-for-query-hiranandani-parliament-interview-9003140%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%20data-sk%3D%5C%22tooltip_parent%5C%22%3Eoutlets%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Trinamool%20Congress%20(TMC)%20MP%20Mahua%20Moitra%20addressed%20the%20cash-for-query%20allegations%20against%20her%2C%20saying%20that%20there%20was%20no%20quid%20pro%20quo%20between%20her%20and%20businessman%20Darshan%20Hiranandani.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShe%20admitted%20that%20she%20had%20given%20her%20Parliament%20login%20ID%20and%20password%20to%20the%20businessman%2C%20to%20have%20someone%20in%20his%20office%20to%20type%20in%20the%20questions%20to%20be%20asked%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha.%20She%20said%20the%20process%20requires%20a%20One-Time%20Password%20(OTP)%2C%20and%20that%20the%20idea%20of%20someone%20else%2C%20in%20this%20case%2C%20Hiranandani%2C%20logged%20into%20her%20account%20and%20posted%20questions%20on%20her%20behalf%20is%20%E2%80%98ludicrous%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20enter%20Parliament%2C%20there%20are%20no%20NIC%20%5BNational%20Informatics%20Centre%5D%20rules%20for%20Parliament.%20No%20MP%20does%20their%20own%20questions%20%E2%80%93%20LAMPs%20(Legislative%20Assistants%20to%20Members%20of%20Parliament)%20do%20it%2C%20or%20interns%20do%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20MP%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fpolitical-pulse%2Fmahua-moitra-cash-for-query-hiranandani-parliament-interview-9003140%2F%5C%22%3Etold%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20question%20and%20answer%20password%20does%20not%20give%20you%20access%20to%20the%20vaults%20of%20the%20RBI%20or%20the%20Budget%20document%2C%20it%20is%20just%20to%20upload%20or%20update%20your%20question.%20An%20OTP%20comes%20to%20your%20mobile%2C%20and%20in%2099%25%20of%20the%20cases%2C%20MPs%20do%20not%20give%20their%20phone%20numbers%20for%20the%20OTP.%20But%20in%20my%20case%2C%20my%20phone%20number%20is%20given%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20became%20an%20MP%20and%20since%20I%20represent%20a%20remote%20constituency%20(Krishnanagar)%2C%20I%20asked%20Darshan%20to%20get%20someone%20in%20his%20office%20to%20type%20down%20the%20question%20and%20upload%20it.%20He%20is%20my%20friend%20and%20I%20do%20not%20think%20there%20is%20anything%20wrong%20with%20it.%20How%20do%20you%20know%20which%20business%20group%20goes%20and%20gives%20questions%20to%20your%20intern%20or%20LAMP%20to%20file%3F%E2%80%A6%20I%20have%20given%20him%20the%20password%20and%20login%20for%20someone%20in%20his%20office%20to%20type%20it%20down%20and%20upload.%20Since%20the%20OTP%20comes%20to%20me%2C%20there%20is%20no%20question%20of%20Darshan%20or%20anyone%20putting%20it%20without%20my%20knowledge.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20%E2%80%98cash-for-query%E2%80%99%20allegation%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20MP%20Nishikant%20Dubey%20approached%20the%20Ethics%20Committee%2C%20alleging%20that%20the%20TMC%20leader%20had%20accepted%20bribes%20and%20favours%20in%20return%20for%20asking%20questions%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20at%20the%20behest%20of%20businessman%20Hiranandani.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMoitra%20responded%20to%20this%20allegation%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20saying%3A%20%E2%80%9CTell%20me%2C%20where%20is%20the%20money%3F%20The%20main%20thing%20to%20prove%20is%20the%20quid%20pro%20quo.%20Darshan%20is%20an%20Indian%20citizen%2C%20he%20runs%20some%20of%20the%20biggest%20IT%20firms%20in%20the%20country%20and%20its%20biggest%20client%20is%20the%20GOI%20(Government%20of%20India).%20So%20he%20cannot%20be%20%E2%80%98anti-national%E2%80%99.%20One%20of%20his%20secretaries%20typed%20the%20questions%20I%20framed%E2%80%A6%20Darshan%20in%20his%20affidavit%20(to%20the%20Ethics%20Committee)%20says%20that%20he%20is%20the%20biggest%20fan%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi.%20Where%20did%20he%20attack%20Adani%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20analysis%20given%20in%20the%20affidavit%20(by%20Jai%20Anant%20Dehadrai)%20of%20my%20questions%20is%20laughable.%20To%20my%20question%20as%20to%20the%20statistics%20regarding%20the%20quality%20of%20service%20provided%20by%20telecom%20companies%2C%20Dehadrai%20has%20written%20as%20analysis%20that%2C%20just%20a%20day%20earlier%2C%20Hiranandani%20had%20hired%20a%20former%20Reliance%20Jio%20executive.%20What%20rubbish%20is%20this%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6%20Adani%20has%20used%20the%20government%2C%20ED%20(Enforcement%20Directorate)%20and%20CBI%20to%20shut%20up%20competitors.%20I%20am%20fully%20within%20my%20rights%20to%20raise%20questions%20against%20Adani%E2%80%A6%20What%20you%20need%20to%20prove%20is%20that%20I%20took%20cash%20for%20this.%20Where%20is%20the%20cash%3F%E2%80%A6%20What%20is%20the%20secret%20answer%20I%20am%20getting%20on%20Adani%20that%20Hiranandani%20could%20not%20get%20on%20his%20own%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShe%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Findia%2Fstory%2Fcash-for-query-claim-mahua-moitra-exclusive-interview-nishikant-dubey-ethics-committee-2454701-2023-10-27%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EIndia%20Today%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20%E2%80%9CNow%20that%20the%20cash-for-query%20has%20fallen%20flat%2C%20this%20is%20being%20made%20out%20to%20be%20some%20great%20issue%20of%20national%20security.%20Mr.%20Dubey%20has%20gone%20to%20the%20press%20and%20said%20that%20it%20is%20a%20national%20security%20issue.%20The%20NIC%20login%20has%20no%20rules%20as%20to%20who%20can%20have%20your%20login.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fas-modi-government-and-adani-train-guns-on-opposition-mp-mahua-moitra-heres-what-we-know-and-dont-know%5C%22%3EAs%20Modi%20Government%20and%20Adani%20Train%20Guns%20on%20Opposition%20MP%20Mahua%20Moitra%2C%20Here%E2%80%99s%20What%20We%20Know%20and%20Don%E2%80%99t%20Know%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Cash%20may%20have%20been%20offered%20to%20not%20question%2C%E2%80%99%20alleges%20Moitra%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIndia%20Today%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%20Moitra%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Findia%2Fstory%2Fmahua-moitra-interview-india-today-cash-for-query-row-2454694-2023-10-27%5C%22%3Eas%20alleging%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%C2%A0%E2%80%9CMr%20Adani%20has%20approached%20me%20via%20two%20Lok%20Sabha%20MPs%20in%20the%20last%20three%20years%20to%20sit%20across%20the%20table%20with%20him%20and%20work%20out%20a%20deal%20I%20have%20refused.%20The%20issue%20is%2C%20he%20was%20giving%20cash%20to%20not%20question.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20that%20she%20refused%20the%20deal%20offered%20to%20her%20to%20sit%20across%20the%20table%20with%20Adani%20and%20%E2%80%9Csort%20it%20out%E2%80%9D.%20She%20added%2C%20saying%20that%20the%20two%20(unnamed)%20MPs%20met%20her%20only%20to%20enable%20a%20meeting%20with%20Adani%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20never%20met%20him%2C%20so%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20what%20he%20was%20offering%20or%20what%20price%20he%20was%20paying.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Trinamool%20leader%20alleged%20that%20she%20was%20approached%20again%20last%20week%20and%20was%20asked%20to%20%E2%80%9Ckeep%20quiet%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20given%20the%20message%3A%20%E2%80%98Please%20end%20this.%20Please%20keep%20quiet%20for%20six%20months%20till%20the%20elections%20are%20over.%20Everything%20will%20be%20fine%20afterwards.%20Even%20if%20you%20want%20to%20attack%20Mr%20Adani%2C%20you%20can%20do%20it%20slightly%2C%20but%20just%20don%E2%80%99t%20take%20the%20Prime%20Minister%E2%80%99s%20name%E2%80%99%2C%E2%80%9D%20Moitra%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20it%20was%20her%20job%20to%20question%20Adani%20and%20she%20would%20continue%20doing%20it.%20She%20alleged%20that%20there%20were%20coal%20scams%20and%20more%20and%20citizens%20were%20paying%20much%20higher%20prices%20for%20coal%2C%20fuel%2C%20tickets%20and%20airports%20due%20to%20irregularities%2C%20she%20would%20continue%20to%20raise.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShe%20dismissed%20the%20allegation%20of%20Darshan%20Hiranandani%E2%80%99s%20clash%20of%20business%20interests%20with%20Adani%20and%20said%20there%20was%20no%20cash%20and%20nothing%20mentioned%20in%20Hiranandani%E2%80%99s%20affidavit.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAdani%2C%20after%20the%20charges%20were%20made%20at%20Opposition%20MP%2C%20issued%20a%20statement%20saying%20%E2%80%9Csome%20groups%20and%20individuals%20have%20been%20working%20overtime%20to%20harm%20our%20name%2C%20goodwill%20and%20market%20standing%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Fbusiness%2Fstory%2Fadani-group-issues-statement-mahua-moitra-bribe-for-questions-row-2449723-2023-10-16%5C%22%3EThe%20Adani%20Group%20spokesperson%20said%20on%20October%2016%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9Cin%20this%20particular%20case%2C%20a%20lawyer%E2%80%99s%20complaint%20reveals%20that%20this%20arrangement%20to%20besmirch%20the%20reputation%20and%20interests%20of%20the%20Adani%20Group%20and%20our%20chairman%20Gautam%20Adani%20has%20been%20in%20place%20since%202018.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Ethics%20Committee%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMoitra%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fethics-committee-summons-mahua-moitra-on-oct-31-ignoring-mps-requests-to-delay-until-festival%5C%22%3Ehas%20sought%20more%20time%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20appear%20before%20the%20Ethics%20Committee%2C%20saying%20that%20owing%20to%20Vijaya%20Dashami%20meetings%20scheduled%20between%20October%2030%20and%20November%204%2C%20she%20cannot%20be%20in%20New%20Delhi%20on%20October%2031.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShe%20further%20said%20that%20Hiranandani%20should%20also%20be%20present%20before%20the%20ethics%20panel%2C%20and%20provide%20%E2%80%9Cverified%20lists%E2%80%9D%20of%20all%20alleged%20gifts%20and%20favours%20that%20the%20TMC%20MP%20is%20alleged%20to%20have%20received.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20one%20scarf%20as%20a%20birthday%20gift%20she%20got%20and%20some%20personal%20cosmetic%20items%2C%20namely%20lipstick%20and%20eye%20shadow%20she%20asked%20for%20when%20he%20rang%20from%20Dubai%20duty-free%20enquiring%20if%20she%20wanted%20anything.%20%E2%80%9CI%20asked%20as%20he%20was%20a%20close%20personal%20friend.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShe%20denied%20he%20helped%20in%20any%20house%20renovation%2C%20showing%20architect%20drawings%20he%20had%20passed%20on%20which%20she%20said%20she%20gave%20to%20the%20CPWD%20engineer%20to%20make%20some%20changes%20in%20her%20official%20home.%20No%20private%20contractor%20was%20hired%2C%20she%20said%2C%20waving%20the%20drawings%20of%20the%20architect%20Hiranandani%20sent%20her%2C%20on%20the%20screen.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698490283000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F08%2F30154328%2FSK9A9999.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmahua-moitra-says-neither-quid-nor-quo-only-slander-all-questions-in-parliament-were-hers%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Keeping%20the%20focus%20of%20questions%20on%20Adani%20she%20raised%20that%20have%20pushed%20the%20Modi%20government%20into%20a%20corner%2C%20she%20says%20she%20was%20sent%20feelers%20to%20%E2%80%98keep%20quiet%E2%80%99%20till%20the%20elections.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmahua-moitra-says-neither-quid-nor-quo-only-slander-all-questions-in-parliament-were-hers%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Israel's%20latest%20ground%20raid%20into%20Gaza%20is%20different%20from%20what%20we've%20seen%20before%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698487380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F10%2F768x432%2Fskynews-israel-airstrikes-gaza_6337492.jpg%3F20231027130254%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fisraels-latest-g