-12994589%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fwe-cant-even-check-on-our-families-life-inside-gaza-after-phone-and-internet-lines-cut-12994589%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22It%20Is%20Not%20Civil%20Servants%E2%80%99%20Job%20to%20%E2%80%98Showcase%E2%80%99%20Govt%20Achievements%3A%20Former%20Cabinet%20Secretary%20Chandrasekhar%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F28134832%2Fkm-chand.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Union%20government%E2%80%99s%20order%20to%20deploy%20civil%20servants%20as%20%E2%80%98Rath%20Prabharis%E2%80%99%20to%20specifically%20promote%20the%20%E2%80%9Cachievements%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20past%20nine%20years%20has%20drawn%20significant%20criticism%20from%20several%20quarters.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fmodi-government-move-to-turn-government-officers-into-rath-prabharis-stirs-storm%5C%22%3Eorder%3C%2Fa%3E%20asks%20every%20ministry%20to%20nominate%20officers%20of%20the%20level%20of%20joint%20secretaries%20and%20below%20in%20each%20of%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20765%20districts%C2%A0to%20%E2%80%9Cshowcase%20the%20achievements%20of%20the%20last%20nine%20years%20of%20Government%20of%20India%E2%80%9D%20between%20November%2020%2C%202023%20and%20January%2025%2C%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESome%20retired%20bureaucrats%20have%20said%20that%20this%20amounts%20to%20the%20wholesale%20politicisation%20of%20the%20civil%20services%2C%20and%20registered%20their%20protest.%20While%20the%20government%20has%20said%20that%20Rath%20Prabharis%20will%20not%20be%20nominated%20in%20the%20five%20states%20headed%20to%20assembly%20polls%20until%20the%20Model%20Code%20of%20Conduct%20is%20in%20place%2C%20this%20will%20only%20provide%20temporary%20relief%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Frath-prabhari-illegal-wholesale-politicisation-civil-services-eas-sarma%5C%22%3Eformer%20IAS%20officer%20E.A.S.%20Sarma%20said%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20spoke%20to%20K.M.%20Chandrasekhar%2C%20who%20retired%20as%20cabinet%20secretary%20in%202011%20and%20served%20under%20Manmohan%20Singh%2C%20about%20his%20views%20on%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20do%20you%20view%20this%20order%3F%20Would%20you%20say%20this%20is%20a%20violation%20of%20the%20Central%20Civil%20Services%20Conduct%20Rules%2C%201964%20which%20says%20government%20servants%20will%20not%20indulge%20in%20political%20activities%3F%20This%20is%20an%20allegation%20being%20made%20by%20opposition%20leaders.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EI%20would%20say%20this%20is%20not%20a%20violation%20of%20the%20conduct%20rules%2C%20because%20government%20servants%20are%20supposed%20to%20follow%20orders%20unless%20they%20are%20against%20the%20law.%20But%20it%20is%20certainly%20not%20in%20good%20taste.%20A%20civil%20servant%E2%80%99s%20job%20is%20to%20implement%20government%20schemes%20and%20deliver%20services.%20At%20best%2C%20if%20there%20are%20issues%20of%20coordination%20with%20the%20states%2C%20officers%20can%20put%20out%20their%20contact%20details%20but%20that%20is%20for%20the%20purposes%20of%20carrying%20out%20their%20duties.%20As%20cabinet%20secretary%2C%20I%20would%20take%20secretaries%20of%20various%20departments%20by%20the%20planeloads%20to%20the%20various%20states%2C%20especially%20the%20weaker%20states%20for%20better%20coordination%20between%20the%20Union%20and%20state%20governments%20and%20better%20delivery%20of%20services.%20We%20would%20resolve%20problems%20on%20the%20spot.%20That%20in%20short%20is%20the%20job%20of%20a%20civil%20servant.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBut%20politicians%20like%20BJP%20IT%20Cell%20head%20Amit%20Malviya%20say%20that%20bureaucrats%20must%20serve%20the%20people%20as%20the%20government%20deems%20fit.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOur%20job%20is%20not%20to%20showcase%20or%20celebrate%20the%20achievements%20of%20the%20government.%20While%20this%20order%20of%20Rath%20Prabharis%20is%20per%20se%20not%20illegal%2C%20it%20is%20definitely%20in%20bad%20taste.%20Projecting%20anyone%20in%20this%20manner%20is%20extraordinary%20and%20I%20have%20never%20heard%20of%20something%20like%20this%20in%20my%20entire%20career.%20Anyway%2C%20officials%20at%20the%20level%20of%20deputy%20director%20or%20director%20are%20too%20junior%20and%20have%20the%20power%20to%20only%20put%20up%20files.%20They%20cannot%20take%20a%20decision%20or%20resolve%20a%20problem%20on%20the%20ground.%20So%20just%20reading%20out%20from%20a%20written%20piece%20of%20paper%20is%20not%20something%20that%20officers%20should%20be%20doing.%20This%20is%20most%20unusual.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThere%20is%20another%20order%20issued%20by%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Defence%20which%20says%20that%20soldiers%20on%20leave%20must%20showcase%20the%20efforts%20of%20the%20government.%20So%20this%20is%20not%20just%20about%20government%20servants.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20again%20is%20a%20ridiculous%20order.%20When%20a%20person%20is%20on%20leave%2C%20they%20cannot%20be%20tasked%20to%20carry%20out%20such%20orders.%20The%20government%20can%20only%20request.%20And%20even%20then%2C%20how%20can%20such%20an%20order%20be%20implemented%3F%20Who%20will%20monitor%20and%20how%20will%20the%20soldier%20know%20the%20fine%20details%20of%20the%20schemes%20of%20the%20government%3F%20If%20a%20person%20is%20on%20leave%2C%20he%20or%20she%20is%20on%20leave.%20If%20a%20person%20is%20asked%20to%20carry%20out%20these%20orders%20then%20he%20or%20she%20cannot%20be%20deemed%20to%20be%20on%20leave.%20Again%20a%20highly%20improper%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIf%20you%20were%20cabinet%20secretary%20now%2C%20what%20would%20you%20do%3F%20And%20it%20is%20easy%20to%20criticise%20when%20an%20officer%20has%20retired%20but%20it%20is%20quite%20a%20different%20thing%20when%20the%20officer%20is%20serving.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EI%20can%20only%20share%20an%20anecdote%20of%20what%20it%20was%20like%20to%20work%20with%20the%20Manmohan%20Singh%20government.%20Once%20I%20called%20the%20prime%20minister%20about%20an%20appointment%20of%20a%20special%20director%20to%20the%20CBI.%20A%20junior%20officer%20was%20being%20appointed%2C%20overlooking%20the%20seniority%20of%20another.%20The%20prime%20minister%20was%20eating%20lunch.%20He%20halted%20his%20meal%2C%20heard%20me%20out%20and%20left%20his%20lunch%20unfinished.%20A%20few%20minutes%20later%2C%20I%20got%20a%20call%20from%20(the%20advisor%20to%20the%20prime%20minister)%20T.K.A.%20Nair%2C%20who%20said%20the%20prime%20minister%20wanted%20to%20see%20the%20two%20of%20us.%20We%20reached%207%2C%20Race%20Course%20Road%2C%20where%20Pulok%20Chatterjee%20(also%20principal%20secretary%20to%20the%20prime%20minister)%20was%20already%20waiting.%20The%20prime%20minister%20immediately%20worked%20out%20a%20solution%20to%20the%20satisfaction%20of%20the%20senior%20CBI%20officer%20and%20gave%20orders%20to%20the%20Department%20of%20Personnel%20and%20Training%20Minister%20Prithviraj%20Chavan%20to%20do%20the%20needful.%20I%20am%20not%20sure%20if%20anyone%20can%20even%20tell%20the%20present%20prime%20minister%20that%20he%20is%20wrong.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698481545000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F28134832%2Fkm-chand.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fcivil-servants-rath-prabharis-km-chandrasekhar-interview%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Wire%20spoke%20to%20K.M.%20Chandrasekhar%20about%20the%20controversy%20over%20the%20Modi%20government%20asking%20ministries%20to%20nominate%20civil%20servants%20as%20'Rath%20Prabharis'.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A16%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fcivil-servants-rath-prabharis-km-chandrasekhar-interview%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22BBC%20reports%20from%20Gaza%20after%20heaviest%20Israeli%20bombing%20yet%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698481388000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F7B2F%2Fproduction%2F_131553513_p0gpbv12.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-middle-east-67248399%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Rushdi%20Abualouf%20reports%20from%20Khan%20Younis%20after%20the%20most%20intense%20bombing%20of%20the%20war%20so%20far.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1538%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fav%2Fworld-middle-east-67248399%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22In%2010%20Years%2C%20Total%20Cargo%20Handled%20by%20Adani%20Ports%20Jumped%20Nearly%20Fourfold%20to%20337%20MT%20in%20FY23%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F07%2FAdani_Mundra_Port_Kutch_Gujarat1.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EWith%20as%20many%20as%2014%20ports%20and%20terminals%2C%20the%20Adani%20Group%20handles%20a%20quarter%20of%20all%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fbusiness%2Fcompanies%2Fadani-ports-handles-highest-ever-rail-cargo-fy23-8613993%2F%5C%22%3Ecargo%20passing%20through%20India%E2%80%99s%20ports%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fexpress-exclusive%2Fon-average-an-adani-port-every-500-km-of-coastline-these-handle-24-of-all-cargo-govt-share-dips-9002772%2F%5C%22%3Ethe%20%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20reported.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAlong%20India%E2%80%99s%205%2C422-kilometre%20coastline%2C%20Adani%20has%20a%20presence%20every%20500%20km%20on%20an%20average%2C%20from%20just%20a%20blip%20on%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20far%20western%20end%2010%20years%20ago%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThree%20top%20officials%2C%20including%20a%20former%20competition%20regulator%2C%20have%20flagged%20risks%20of%20market%20concentration%20in%20the%20ports%20industry%2C%20highlighting%20Adani%E2%80%99s%20phenomenal%20expansion%20in%20the%20last%2010%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%2010%20years%2C%20the%20total%20cargo%20handled%20by%20Adani%20ports%20jumped%20nearly%20fourfold%20to%20337%20million%20tonnes%20in%20FY23.%20Its%20volumes%20grew%20at%20a%20compounded%20annual%20growth%20rate%20of%2014%25%20against%20the%20industry%E2%80%99s%204%25.%20If%20Adani%E2%80%99s%20share%20is%20removed%2C%20the%20latter%20figure%20falls%20to%20barely%202.7%25%2C%20the%20newspaper%20said%20in%20its%20investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20group%E2%80%99s%20market%20share%20in%20total%20cargo%20handled%20has%20nearly%20tripled%20from%20around%209%25%20in%202013%20to%20about%2024%25%20in%202023%3B%20that%20of%20Central%20government-controlled%20ports%20dropped%20to%20around%2054.5%25%20from%2058.5%25%20in%202013.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAmongst%20ports%20that%20are%20not%20under%20the%20Union%20government%2C%20Adani%E2%80%99s%20market%20share%20has%20crossed%20the%2050%25%20mark%2C%20the%20daily%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETherefore%2C%20Adani%20Ports%20and%20Special%20Economic%20Zone%20Ltd%20(APSEZ)%E2%80%99s%20coastal%20network%20competes%20with%20the%20Union%20government%E2%80%99s%20over%2012%20ports.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20fact%2C%20part%20of%20the%20rise%20in%20Adani%20Group%E2%80%99s%20market%20share%20in%20the%20ports%20sector%20%E2%80%93%20from%209%25%20to%2024%25%20in%2010%20years%20%E2%80%93%20has%20come%20at%20the%20cost%20of%20the%20Union%20government-controlled%20ports%20(called%20%E2%80%98major%20ports%E2%80%99%20in%20industry%20parlance)%20whose%20cargo%20share%20has%20fallen%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20newspaper%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20a%20concern%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20top%20economic%20ministry%20official%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Indian%20Express.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Fadanis-acquisitions-the-inorganic-strategy-behind-the-purchase-of-gangavaram-port%5C%22%3EAdani%E2%80%99s%20Acquisitions%3A%20The%20%E2%80%98Inorganic%20Strategy%E2%80%99%20Behind%20the%20Purchase%20of%20Gangavaram%20Port%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThese%20section%20of%20government%20officials%20and%20regulators%20pointed%20out%C2%A0that%20this%20growth%20has%20been%20through%20the%20inorganic%20route.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CCargo%20handling%20data%20analysed%20by%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20shows%20that%20the%20ports%20acquired%20over%20the%20last%20decade%20by%20the%20Adani%20Group%20account%20for%20more%20than%20a%20third%20of%20the%20total%20cargo%20volumes%20(123.7%20million%20tonnes%20of%20337%20million%20tonnes%2C%20or%2037%25)%20handled%20by%20the%20company.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSuch%20a%20growth%20model%20compounds%20the%20concerns%20about%20the%20growing%20concentration%20risk%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20same%20official%20told%20the%20daily.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20growing%20dominance%20of%20a%20single%20player%20along%20the%20entire%20coastline%2C%20from%20west%20to%20east%2C%20could%20potentially%20lead%20to%20a%20gradual%20weakening%20of%20the%20negotiating%20leverage%20held%20by%20shipping%20companies%2C%20particularly%20in%20certain%20geographic%20regions%2C%20the%20report%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F25192401%2FSecretary_Kerry_greets_Executive_Chairman_Adani_before_meeting_with_Indian_CEOs_amid_Vibrant_Gujarat_Summit.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221097%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F25192401%2FSecretary