even%20a%20second%2C%20that%20the%20Hamas%20terrorists%20are%20some%20kind%20of%20freedom%20fighters.%20They%20are%20monsters%2C%20far%20below%20the%20threshold%20of%20true%20human%20beings.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20this%20war%2C%20which%20is%20still%20in%20danger%20of%20expanding%20to%20other%20fronts%2C%20has%20already%20revealed%20the%20complete%20collapse%20of%20the%20regnant%20Israeli%20vision%20of%20reality%20and%20of%20the%20policies%20Israel%20has%20pursued%20over%20the%20last%20several%20decades.%20That%20collapse%20was%20imminent%20anyway%2C%20though%20not%20everyone%20could%20see%20it.%20Israel%20has%20indulged%20in%20a%20dark%20chimera%2C%20an%20interlocking%20sheaf%20of%20delusions%20that%20somehow%20kept%20up%20an%20appearance%20of%20having%20some%20potential%20link%20to%20reality.%20It%20is%20not%20difficult%20to%20spell%20this%20out.%20I%E2%80%99ll%20begin%20with%20the%20easy%20part.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3E1)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20present%20extreme%20right-wing%20government%20has%20compounded%20the%20cumulating%20disaster%20of%20recent%20years%2C%20not%20least%20by%20attempting%20to%20undermine%20the%20basic%20institutions%20of%20Israeli%20democracy%20as%20well%20as%20the%20social%20fabric.%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%2C%20who%20has%20done%20more%20damage%20to%20the%20state%20of%20Israel%20than%20anyone%20else%20in%20living%20memory%2C%20has%20brought%20the%20country%20to%20the%20brink%20of%20civil%20war.%20He%20has%20attacked%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Famid-protests-israeli-parliament-approves-contentious-judicial-reform-law%5C%22%3Ejudicial%20system%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%93%20particularly%20but%20not%20only%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%20He%20has%20replaced%20competent%20experts%20and%20bureaucrats%20in%20the%20civil%20service%20with%20sycophants%20and%20toadies%20lacking%20any%20relevant%20training%20or%20knowledge.%20He%20has%20undermined%20the%20army%2C%20as%20everyone%20in%20the%20higher%20echelons%20of%20the%20security%20establishment%20warned%20him%20months%20ago.%20He%20has%20ruined%20the%20economy%2C%20including%20its%20brightest%20hope%2C%20the%20high-tech%20industry.%20He%20has%20fomented%20hatred%20among%20the%20communities%20that%20make%20up%20Israeli%20society%20and%20created%20a%20ragamuffin%20mob%20of%20violent%20%E2%80%9CBibists%E2%80%9D%20akin%20to%20the%20Fascists%20and%20marauding%20gangs%20familiar%20from%20many%20authoritarian%20regimes.%20The%20result%20of%20this%20systemic%20erosion%20of%20the%20state%2C%20on%20all%20levels%2C%20was%20clearly%20apparent%20in%20the%20lethal%20failure%20of%20the%20armed%20forces%20on%20October%207%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20In%20effect%2C%20the%20army%2C%20including%20the%20intelligence%20branches%2C%20indeed%20the%20state%20apparatus%20as%20a%20whole%2C%20evaporated%2C%20leaving%20thousands%20of%20ordinary%20civilians%20to%20be%20murdered%20at%20the%20hands%20of%20Hamas.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20apart%20from%20the%20disastrous%20influence%20of%20the%20present%20government%20on%20all%20aspects%20of%20life%20in%20Israel%2C%20there%20was%20an%20idea%2C%20or%20a%20set%20of%20ideas%2C%20at%20the%20heart%20of%20the%20Netanyahu%20project.%20More%20on%20that%20below.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F18123957%2FF8aEEn1WYAAtWt0.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F18123957%2FF8aEEn1WYAAtWt0.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F18123957%2FF8aEEn1WYAAtWt0-300x159.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F18123957%2FF8aEEn1WYAAtWt0-1024x544.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-680601%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22637%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIsrael%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu.%20Photo%3A%20X%2F%40netanyahu%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3E2)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Gaza.%20On%20the%20immediate%20horizon%20we%20have%20the%20problem%20of%20Gaza%20and%20Hamas%20rule%20there.%20It%20is%20important%20to%20put%20an%20end%20to%20the%20Hamas%20hold%20on%20power%2C%20just%20as%20it%20was%20important%2C%20not%20so%20long%20ago%2C%20for%20the%20US%20and%20their%20allies%20to%20eliminate%20ISIS%20and%20al-Qaeda%20as%20military%20forces.%20Hamas%20belongs%20in%20that%20list%20of%20evil%20movements.%20Here%2C%20a%20little%20recent%20history%20should%20be%20recalled.%20Gaza%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20densely%20populated%20places%20on%20earth%3B%20two%20and%20a%20half%20million%20people%20are%20crammed%20into%20an%20area%20of%20365%20square%20kilometres%2C%20most%20of%20it%20thickly%20built-up%20urban%20sites.%20The%20vast%20majority%20of%20the%20population%20there%20are%20refugee%20families%20from%20the%201948%20war%20(that%20is%2C%20third%20or%20even%20fourth%20generations%20of%20those%20families).%20In%202005%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Ariel%20Sharon%20removed%20the%20Israeli%20settlements%20that%20had%20been%20placed%20in%20the%20midst%20of%20this%20dense%20Palestinian%20population%3B%20typically%2C%20he%20did%20this%20as%20a%20unilateral%20Israeli%20decision%2C%20with%20almost%20no%20coordination%2C%20and%20certainly%20no%20mutual%20agreement%20with%20the%20Palestinian%20Authority%20(ruling%20in%20Area%20A%20of%20the%20West%20Bank).%20There%20was%20bad%20blood%20between%20Fatah%2C%20the%20central%20body%20of%20the%20Palestinian%20national%20movement%2C%20and%20Hamas.%20In%20June%202007%2C%20in%20a%20brief%2C%20bloody%20campaign%2C%20Hamas%20took%20control%20of%20Gaza%20and%20evicted%20Fatah%20and%20the%20Palestinian%20Authority.%20Its%20rule%20since%20then%20has%20been%20characterised%20by%20corruption%2C%20a%20fierce%20fundamentalist%20ideology%2C%20and%20totalitarian%20suppression%20of%20any%20rivals%3B%20also%20by%20the%20explicit%20goal%20of%20destroying%20the%20state%20of%20Israel.%20Despite%20that%2C%20for%20the%20last%20decade%20or%20more%2C%20Netanyahu%20has%20strengthened%20Hamas%20by%20allowing%20huge%20monetary%20transfers%20(in%20billions%20of%20dollars)%20to%20them%20from%20Qatar%2C%20among%20other%20measures.%20The%20logic%20of%20this%20odd%2C%20not%20to%20say%20idiotic%2C%20policy%20was%20that%20by%20building%20up%20Hamas%2C%20Israel%20was%20weakening%20the%20Palestinian%20Authority%20still%20further%20and%2C%20having%20thus%20divided%20the%20Palestinian%20population%20between%20these%20two%20poles%2C%20could%20prevent%20the%20very%20possibility%20that%20a%20Palestinian%20state%20could%20ever%20emerge%20on%20the%20West%20Bank.%20Netanyahu%20has%20explicitly%20articulated%20this%20approach%20at%20various%20times%20in%20the%20course%20of%20those%20years%2C%20which%20were%20also%20characterised%20by%20periodic%20%E2%80%9Crounds%E2%80%9D%20(%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Esevev%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20Hebrew)%20of%20fighting%20between%20Israel%20and%20Hamas%20meant%20to%20deter%20Hamas%20from%20attacking%20Israel%20for%20some%20limited%20period%20of%20time.%20These%20rounds%20of%20fighting%20failed%20utterly%20to%20generate%20such%20deterrence%2C%20as%20we%20can%20see%20from%20the%20events%20of%20October%207%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0this%20year.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAlthough%20Netanyahu%20is%20sometimes%20seen%20as%20a%20straightforward%20opportunist%20focused%20only%20on%20his%20own%20personal%20benefit%2C%20it%20is%20a%20mistake%20to%20think%20that%20he%20has%20no%20overriding%20plan%20for%20Israel%20and%20Palestine.%20He%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fpalestine-israel-netanyahu-annexation-plan%5C%22%3Espelt%20this%20out%20for%20all%20to%20hear%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He%20thinks%20that%20Israel%20can%2C%20indeed%20must%2C%20extirpate%20the%20Palestinian%20national%20movement%20completely%2C%20at%20the%20same%20time%20settling%20the%20West%20Bank%20with%20Israelis%20and%20eventually%20annexing%20much%20or%20even%20all%20of%20it%20to%20Israel%20(possibly%20along%20with%20the%20expulsion%20of%20the%20Palestinian%20population%20there).%20This%20leads%20to%20the%20heart%20of%20the%20conflict%20and%20to%20the%20present%20catastrophic%20situation.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fhistory-israel-palestine-conflict-five-charts%5C%22%3EUnderstanding%20the%20History%20of%20the%20Israeli-Palestinian%20Conflict%20in%20Five%20Charts%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3E3)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Stated%20simply%3A%20Israel%20has%20no%20viable%20future%20unless%20it%20reaches%20some%20form%20of%20accommodation%20and%20rapprochement%20with%20the%20Palestinian%20people%2C%20who%20share%20the%20land%20west%20of%20the%20Jordan%20River%20with%20Israeli%20Jews.%20That%20rapprochement%20must%20enable%20institutional%20and%20political%20expression%20for%20Palestinian%20national%20aspirations%2C%20such%20as%20the%20state%20of%20Israel%20has%20created%20for%20the%20Jews.%20The%20two%20populations%2C%20Jewish%20and%20Palestinian%2C%20are%20now%20more%20or%20less%20at%20parity%20(over%20five%20million%20in%20Gaza%20and%20the%20West%20Bank%2C%20and%20another%20two%20million%20or%20more%20who%20are%20Palestinian%20citizens%20of%20the%20State%20of%20Israel%2C%20compared%20with%20roughly%20eight%20million%20Jews).%20In%20effect%2C%20a%20binational%20state%20already%20exists%2C%20but%20in%20the%20unworkable%20form%20of%20apartheid%20rule%20over%20the%20Palestinian%20West%20Bank.%20Note%2C%20however%2C%20that%20large%20pockets%20of%20friendly%20co-existence%20are%20in%20evidence%20all%20over%20Israel%3A%20Palestinians%20and%20Israelis%20work%20peacefully%20side%20by%20side%20in%20hospitals%20and%20health%20services%2C%20in%20the%20restaurant%20industry%2C%20in%20the%20transportation%20network%2C%20in%20other%20service%20sectors%2C%20in%20construction%20and%20maintenance%20of%20infrastructures%2C%20and%20so%20on.%20To%20take%20only%20one%20example%3A%20without%20Palestinian%20doctors%2C%20nurses%2C%20and%20orderlies%2C%20the%20Israeli%20health%20system%20would%20break%20down%20within%20hours.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20West%20Bank%20is%20divided%20into%20three%20areas%20(under%20the%20Oslo%20agreements)%3A%20Area%20A%2C%20under%20full%20Palestinian%20control%3B%20Area%20B%2C%20under%20joint%20Israeli%20and%20Palestinian%20control%3B%20and%20Area%20C%2C%20under%20full%20Israeli%20control.%20However%2C%20in%20practice%2C%20Israel%20does%20whatever%20she%20wants%20on%20the%20West%20Bank%E2%80%94planting%20more%20and%20more%20Israeli%20settlements%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fjerusalem-is-ablaze-again-and-israels-growing-settler-movement-was-the-trigger%5C%22%3Eterrorising%20the%20Palestinian%20civilian%20population%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20intruding%20whenever%20she%20feels%20the%20need%20to%20into%20Areas%20A%20and%20B%2C%20and%20so%20on.%20In%20part%2C%20this%20asymmetrical%20arrangement%20reflects%20considerable%20structural%20weakness%20and%20ineptitude%20on%20the%20part%20of%20the%20Palestinian%20Authority%3B%20Israel%20has%20also%20systematically%20eroded%20the%20institutions%20put%20in%20place%20in%20Area%20A%2C%20with%20the%20exception%20of%20the%20Palestinian%20security%20forces%20who%20are%2C%20in%20effect%2C%20sub-contractors%20for%20Israeli%20security.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20the%20core%20of%20the%20matter%20is%20the%20nature%20and%20telos%20of%20the%20occupation%20itself.%20We%20have%2C%20today%2C%20a%20situation%20in%20which%20Israeli%20Jews%2C%20within%20the%20Green%20Line%20and%20also%20Israeli%20settlers%20on%20the%20West%20Bank%2C%20enjoy%20all%20privileges%20and%20basic%20human%20rights%2C%20while%20Palestinians%20on%20the%20West%20Bank%20have%20no%20human%20rights%20at%20all%E2%80%94no%20legal%20recourse%2C%20no%20protection%20from%20violent%20settlers%20and%20(all%20too%20often%20now)%20soldiers%20and%20police%2C%20no%20political%20representation%2C%20no%20freedom%20of%20speech%2C%20no%20freedom%20of%20movement%2C%20no%20personal%20security%2C%20and%20so%20on.%20This%20reality%2C%20transparent%20to%20anyone%20who%20goes%20into%20the%20West%20Bank%20with%20open%20eyes%2C%20is%20becoming%20more%20and%20more%20cruel%20and%20oppressive%20by%20the%20day%2C%20or%20by%20the%20hour.%20In%20the%20last%20few%20weeks%2C%20extraordinarily%20violent%20Israeli%20settlers%2C%20motivated%20by%20a%20messianic%20and%20apocalyptic%20ideology%2C%20have%20succeeded%20in%20emptying%20out%20whole%20Palestinian%20villages%20in%20the%20central%20West%20Bank%20%E2%80%93%20a%20form%20of%20ethnic%20cleansing%20under%20the%20aegis%20of%20the%20army%20and%20the%20government.%20I%20have%20personal%20experience%20in%20several%20of%20these%20villages%2C%20and%20I%20have%20seen%20the%20endless%20harassment%20by%20hate-filled%20settlers%20that%20left%20the%20villagers%20little%20choice%20but%20to%20leave.%20A%20second%20Nakba%20%E2%80%93%20the%20word%20refers%20to%20the%20catastrophe%20of%20exile%20that%20hundreds%20of%20thousands%20of%20Palestinians%20suffered%20in%201948%2C%20some%20by%20fleeing%20the%20battlefields%20and%20some%20through%20forced%20evictions%20by%20the%20Israeli%20army%20%E2%80%93%20is%20already%20underway.%20It%20is%20largely%20under%20the%20radar%20of%20the%20international%20community%20and%20even%20the%20Israeli%20press%2C%20which%20is%20occupied%20with%20other%20matters%2C%20including%20the%20war.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENo%20society%20can%20continue%20to%20function%20if%20all%20rights%20and%20privileges%20are%20the%20sole%20prerogatives%20of%20one%20section%20of%20the%20populace%20while%20the%20rest%20are%20denied%20them.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20large%20part%20of%20the%20Israeli%20electorate%2C%20identified%20mainly%20with%20the%20religious%20right%2C%20accepts%20and%20supports%20the%20occupation%20and%20the%20discriminatory%20regime%20that%20it%20has%20put%20in%20place.%20They%20believe%20that%20the%20Land%20of%20Israel%20belongs%20uniquely%20to%20the%20Jews%20by%20virtue%20of%20God%E2%80%99s%20command%20(they%20like%20to%20ignore%20the%20Bible%E2%80%99s%20warnings%20that%20the%20land%20may%20be%20lost%20if%20the%20Jews%20fail%20to%20act%20in%20accordance%20with%20moral%20standards).%20A%20majority%20of%20Israeli%20Jews%20do%20not%2C%20however%2C%20see%20things%20like%20that.%20Even%20now%2C%20despite%20the%20clear%20shift%20to%20the%20right%20in%20Israeli%20politics%2C%20the%20mainstream%20is%20by%20no%20means%20committed%20to%20the%20annexationist%20plans%20of%20the%20government%20and%20the%20religious%20Zionists.%20In%20theory%2C%20the%20mainstream%20could%20well%20support%20a%20peace%20agreement%2C%20including%20a%20withdrawal%20from%20most%20of%20the%20West%20Bank%2C%20that%20met%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20real%20security%20concerns.%20Reliable%20opinion%20polls%20in%20the%20Palestinian%20West%20Bank%20and%2C%20interestingly%2C%20in%20Gaza%20consistently%20show%20a%20similar%20majority%20in%20favour%20of%20some%20kind%20of%20workable%20agreement.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIs%20such%20a%20solution%20likely%20to%20emerge%20at%20some%20point%3F%20No%20one%20can%20say.%20I%20myself%20think%20that%20the%20American%20plan%2C%20hinted%20at%20by%20President%20Joe%20Biden%E2%80%99s%20speech%20in%20Israel%20earlier%20this%20month%20and%20reaffirmed%20on%20October%2025%2C%20is%20to%20create%20a%20regional%20settlement%20in%20West%20Asia%20that%20will%20include%20a%20resolution%20of%20Palestinian%20issues.%20What%20is%20certain%20is%20that%20Netanyahu%E2%80%99s%20attempt%20to%20sweep%20the%20Palestinian%20national%20movement%20under%20the%20rug%20while%20attempting%20to%20make%20peace%20agreements%20with%20other%20Arab%20states%20such%20as%20Saudi%20Arabia%20will%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Famid-war-israels-warming-ties-with-saudi-arabia-on-hold%2Fvideo-67215323%23%3A~%3Atext%3DBefore%2520Israel%2520declared%2520war%2520on%2Chave%2520been%2520put%2520on%2520ice.%5C%22%3Enever%20materialise%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%E2%80%99s%20been%20tried%20before%2C%20more%20than%20once%2C%20without%20success.%20The%20events%20in%20Gaza%20this%20month%20are%20a%20decisive%20indication%20of%20this%20basic%20fact.%20A%20conceptual%20revolution%20is%20needed%20in%20Israel%20in%20light%20of%20the%20tragic%20results%20of%20policies%20serving%20the%20hyper-nationalist%20and%20religious%20right.%20Similarly%2C%20the%20prevalent%20notion%20that%20the%20Israeli-Palestinian%20conflict%20can%20be%20%E2%80%9Cmanaged%2C%E2%80%9D%20on%20a%20low%20burner%2C%20so%20to%20speak%2C%20has%20been%20exposed%20as%20false.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F06%2F07142954%2FFlag-Of-Palestine-Arab-Man-Waving-1081797.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Palestine%20Flag.%20Credit%3A%20Wikimedia%20Commons%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F06%2F07142954%2FFlag-Of-Palestine-Arab-Man-Waving-1081797.jpg%201280w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F06%2F07142954%2FFlag-Of-Palestine-Arab-Man-Waving-1081797-300x225.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F06%2F07142954%2FFlag-Of-Palestine-Arab-Man-Waving-1081797-768x576.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F06%2F07142954%2FFlag-Of-Palestine-Arab-Man-Waving-1081797-1024x768.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-257897%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EPalestine%20flag.%20Photo%3A%20Ahmed%20Abu%20Hameeda%20ahmed96%2FWikimedia%20Commons%2C%20CC0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3E4)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20There%20is%20one%20more%20element%20to%20be%20added%20to%20the%20above%20analysis%2C%20which%20in%20any%20case%20needs%20to%20be%20amplified%20and%20far%20more%20nuanced.%20Only%20fools%20think%20that%20the%20predicament%20in%20Israel-Palestine%20is%20simple%20and%20easily%20soluble%2C%20or%20that%20either%20of%20the%20two%20sides%20holds%20a%20monopoly%20on%20good%20or%20evil.%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20existential%20fears%20are%20not%20without%20a%20basis%20in%20reality.%20Palestinian%20moderates%20have%2C%20historically%2C%20often%20been%20vanquished%20by%20the%20extremist%20fundamentalists.%20But%20if%20Israel%20is%20to%20have%20any%20kind%20of%20livable%20future%2C%20that%20is%2C%20a%20future%20worth%20living%20for%2C%20it%20has%20to%20revert%2C%20for%20its%20own%20sake%2C%20to%20the%20classical%2C%20humanistic%2C%20moderate%20values%20of%20Jewish%20civilisation%2C%20which%20also%20underly%20the%20democratic%20framework%20of%20the%20state%E2%80%94the%20framework%20Netanyahu%20has%20tried%20hard%20to%20destroy.%20Contrary%20to%20what%20some%20political%20scientists%20like%20to%20say%20(including%20some%20that%20I%20know%20personally)%2C%20the%20moral%20basis%20of%20any%20polity%20is%20crucial%20to%20its%20survival%2C%20especially%20under%20conditions%20of%20violent%20conflict.%20Indeed%2C%20the%20ethical%20foundation%20may%20ultimately%20be%20more%20important%20than%20the%20standard%20calculations%20of%20naked%20power%20and%20power-driven%20interests.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWith%20some%20justice%2C%20the%20Jews%20may%20claim%20to%20have%20invented%20human%20rights%20as%20we%20think%20of%20them%20today.%20In%20the%20home%20where%20I%20grew%20up%2C%20I%20was%20taught%20that%20the%20essence%20of%20Judaism%20lies%20in%20the%20memory%20that%20we%20were%20once%20slaves%20in%20Egypt%3B%20we%20know%20what%20it%20means%2C%20what%20it%20feels%20like%2C%20to%20be%20a%20slave%3B%20hence%20we%20will%20never%2C%20ever%2C%20enslave%20another%20people.%20Unfortunately%2C%20that%20axiom%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20very%20far%20from%20the%20reality%20of%20the%20occupation.%20Somewhat%20surprisingly%2C%20however%2C%20ethical%20values%2C%20even%20in%20the%20midst%20of%20severe%20conflict%2C%20can%20also%20serve%20political%20self-interest.%20It%20is%20in%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20cardinal%20interest%20to%20end%20the%20occupation%20and%20to%20create%20conditions%20for%20a%20peace%20rooted%20in%20mutuality%20and%20equality%20with%20Palestinians%2C%20in%20our%20own%20deepest%20and%20most%20authentic%20values%2C%20and%20in%20the%20aspirations%20of%20the%20Palestinian%20moderate%20mainstream%20insofar%20as%20the%20latter%20is%20still%20intact.%20I%20believe%20it%20is%2C%20but%20every%20day%20that%20the%20occupation%20continues%20on%20its%20destructive%20course%20eats%20away%20at%20that%20belief.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOf%20course%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20certainly%20possible%20that%20when%20this%20war%20is%20over%2C%20Netanyahu%20will%20hang%20on%20to%20power%20in%20some%20crooked%20way%2C%20and%20Israel%20will%20revert%20to%20the%20untenable%20policies%20of%20the%20last%20few%20years%20until%20the%20next%20cycle%20of%20violence%20bursts%20the%20bubble%20again.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fdavid-shulman%5C%22%3EDavid%20Shulman%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20professor%20at%20the%20Hebrew%20University%20of%20Jerusalem.%20He%20is%20an%20activist%20in%20Ta%E2%80%99ayush%2C%20Arab-Jewish%20Partnership.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698473058000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.t