%20won%E2%80%99t%20agree)%20syndrome.%20My%20parents%20are%20still%20angry%2C%20but%20I%20know%20they%E2%80%99ll%20come%20around%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Dhananjaya.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20founders%20say%20that%20they%20did%20not%20draw%20a%20salary%20for%20the%20first%2014%20months%2C%20and%20initially%2C%20they%20faced%20challenges%20in%20convincing%20customers%20and%20finding%20investors.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20industry%20is%20dominated%20by%20the%20mafia.%20It%E2%80%99s%20tough%20to%20approach%20them%20and%20seek%20a%20partnership.%20Moreover%2C%20we%20started%20our%20company%20during%20a%20funding%20winter%20(a%20time%20when%20venture%20capital%20was%20less)%20and%20had%20to%20pool%20in%20our%20own%20savings.%20The%20biggest%20challenge%20though%2C%20was%20educating%20people%20about%20our%20services%20and%20gaining%20their%20trust.%20We%20didn%E2%80%99t%20do%20advertisements%20for%20the%20same%20but%20have%20worked%20on%20building%20their%20trust%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Dhananjaya.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETheir%20goal%20is%20now%20to%20expand%20across%20the%20country%20and%20become%20the%20go-to%20parking%20solution%20for%20Indians.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20anyone%20to%20worry%20about%20parking%20when%20they%20go%20out.%20We%20want%20them%20to%20have%20a%20good%20time.%20The%20risk%20is%20on%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20remarks.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESources%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%20%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthepatriot.in%2Freports%2Fdelhis-mega-parking-crisis-10121%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Delhi%E2%80%99s%20mega%20parking%20crisis%E2%80%99%3C%2Fa%3E%20Published%20on%2021%20June%2C%202019%20Courtesy%20The%20Patriot%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698416550000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F