%20of%20Remote%20Sensing%20(IIRS)%2C%20a%20division%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F308574%2Fchennai-space-tech-startup-agnikul-behind-indias-first-3d-printed-rockets-isro-launchpad%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIndian%20Space%20Research%20Organisation%20(ISRO)%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20has%20recently%20unveiled%20an%20opportunity%20for%20individuals%20interested%20in%20advancing%20their%20knowledge%20in%20Remote%20Sensing%2C%20Geographical%20Information%20System%20(GIS)%2C%20and%20Global%20Navigation%20Satellite%20System%20(GNSS)%20technologies.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20certification%20course%20is%20designed%20to%20cater%20to%20a%20diverse%20range%20of%20participants%2C%20including%20students%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F332918%2Fisro-announces-job-openings-for-scientists-salaries-up-to-rs-79662-per-month%2F%5C%22%3Etechnical%20and%20scientific%20personnel%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20university%20faculty%2C%20researchers%2C%20and%20professionals%20in%20related%20fields.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThings%20to%20know%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cul%3E%20%3Cli%3EThe%20programme%20covers%20the%20practical%20application%20of%20remote%20sensing%20and%20GIS%20in%20various%20sectors%20%E2%80%94%20including%20agriculture%2C%20forestry%2C%20ecology%2C%20geoscience%2C%20marine%20and%20atmospheric%20sciences%2C%20urban%20and%20regional%20studies%2C%20and%20water%20resources.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EParticipants%20will%20have%20access%20to%20PDF%20lectures%2C%20recorded%20video%20lectures%2C%20open-source%20software%2C%20and%20demonstration%20handouts%2C%20accessible%20via%20the%20E-CLASS%20and%20ISRO%20Learning%20Management%20System.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EThere%20are%20a%20total%20of%2010%2C000%20seats%20available%20for%20the%20entire%20comprehensive%20course%2C%20and%205%2C000%20more%20seats%20for%20individual%20modules.%20Additionally%2C%20nodal%20centre%20coordinators%20are%20allocated%2025%20seats%20for%20each%20course.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EParticipants%20will%20get%20a%20course%20completion%20certificate%20on%20completing%20at%20least%2070%20percent%20of%20the%20total%20session%20hours.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3C%2Ful%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20to%20apply%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cul%3E%20%3Cli%3EUndergraduate%20and%20postgraduate%20students%20(any%20year)%2C%20technical%20and%20scientific%20staff%20from%20central%20or%20state%20governments%2C%20faculty%20and%20researchers%20from%20universities%20and%20institutions%2C%20and%20other%20professionals%20in%20technical%20and%20scientific%20domains.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EInterested%20individuals%20can%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Felearning.iirs.gov.in%2Fedusatregistration%2Fstudent%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eregister%20individually%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20through%20their%20respective%20nodal%20centres%20before%20the%20application%20deadline.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3C%2Ful%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EImportant%20dates%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cul%3E%20%3Cli%3ECourse%20duration%3A%206%20to%2017%20November%2C%202023%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3ERegistration%20open%20date%3A%2016%20October%2C%202023%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3ERegistration%20closing%20date%3A%203%20November%2C%202023%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3C%2Ful%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EFor%20more%20details%2C%20check%20the%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.iirs.gov.in%2Fiirs%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fpdf%2F2023%2FBrochure_of_122th_Course.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Eofficial%20notification%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698410192000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D333130%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Indian%20Institute%20of%20Remote%20Sensing%20(IIRS)%2C%20a%20division%20of%20the%20Indian%20Space%20Research%20Organisation%20(ISRO)%2C%20has%20designed%20a%20free%20online%20certification%20course%20on%20remote%20sensing%2C%20geographical%20information%20system%2C%20and%20GNSS%20technologies.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Pranita%20Bhat%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22This%20100-Yo%20Heritage%20Fort%20in%20Kutch%20Is%20Home%20to%20a%20First-Of-Its-Kind%20CBSE%20School%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETitle%20picture%20courtesy%3A%20Ipsita%20Paul.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20night%20quietens%20under%20the%20moon%20as%20the%20sky%20blue%20table%20comes%20out%20of%20the%20vintage%20dining%20hall.%20The%20chairs%2C%20candles%20and%20the%20crockery%20is%20laid%20out%20for%20the%20Gujarati%20flavours%20to%20shine%20through%20in%20every%20bowl.%20Krutarthsinh%20M%20Jadeja%E2%80%99s%2085-year-old%20mother%20receives%20the%20guests%20with%20garlands%2C%20applies%20a%20%3Cem%3Eteeka%3C%2Fem%3E%20on%20their%20forehead%2C%20and%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CGod%20bless%20you.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20mother%20has%20always%20welcomed%20the%20guests.%20It%E2%80%99s%20our%20tradition.%20She%20says%20that%20we%20must%20pray%20and%20dine%20together%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Krutarthsinh.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20otherwise%20bleak%20Kutchi%20village%2C%20the%20sloped%20road%20bends%20to%20an%20arched%20gate%20fixed%20with%20iron%20nails.%20This%20was%20done%20to%20keep%20elephants%20and%20enemies%20from%20invading%20the%20property.%20Sitting%20on%20a%20mound%2C%20the%20small%20manor%20watches%20over%20the%20six%20generations%20that%20have%20lived%20here%20for%20118%20years.%20The%20bowed%20branches%20of%20Bougainvillea%20engulf%20the%20suites%20here%20and%20the%20%3Cem%3Ejharokhas%3C%2Fem%3E%20(the%20sitting%20windows%20protruding%20outwards%20from%20a%20building)%20articulate%20heritage%20fervour%20even%20from%20a%20distance.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EKrutarthsinh%2C%20the%20ever-smiling%20host%2C%20is%20now%20taking%20care%20of%20this%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F329447%2Fdevra-homestay-in-udaipur-barren-land-to-heritage-property%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eancestral%20property%3C%2Fa%3E%20historically%20known%20as%20the%20Darbargadh%20in%20Devpur%20village%20which%20is%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F270912%2Fchaturbhuj-temple-in-gwalior-has-worlds-oldest-zero-symbol%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E30%20km%20from%20Bhuj%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20is%20now%20known%20commercially%20as%20the%20Devpur%20Homestay.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20a%20few%20rooms%20still%20inhabited%20by%20the%20Jadeja%20family%2C%20the%20vintage%20rooms%20are%20now%20rewriting%20new%20stories%20with%20guests%20having%20access%20to%20various%20suites%20in%20its%20%3Cem%3EMardana%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3EZenana%20%3C%2Fem%3E(separate%20male%20and%20female%20quarters%20as%20used%20to%20be%20the%20norm%20back%20in%20the%20day)%20quarters.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20the%20property%20also%20houses%20a%20CBSE%20school%20on%20the%20grounds%20for%20students%20up%20to%20class%2010.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20832px)%20100vw%2C%20832px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FP_20171001_092314_HDR_11zon-1698325871.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22832%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22One%20of%20the%20study%20areas%20in%20the%20Gulabi%20Mehdi.%20Picture%20courtesy%3A%20Krutarthsinh%20Jadeja.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FP_20171001_092314_HDR_11zon-1698325871.jpg%20832w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FP_20171001_092314_HDR_11zon-1698325871-300x225.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%