%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F332112%2Fisro-chandrayaan-3-project-director-p-veeramuthuvel-gaganyaan-tamil-nadu%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIndian%20Space%20Research%20Organisation%20(ISRO)%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20inviting%20applications%20for%20the%20posts%20of%20%E2%80%98Scientist%2FEngineer%20(SC)%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20a%20total%20of%2010%20job%20vacancies%20available%20%E2%80%94%20one%20vacancy%20each%20in%20the%20disciplines%20of%20polymer%20science%20and%20engineering%2Frubber%20technology%20and%20MSc%20agriculture%20(horticulture%2Fforestry)%2C%20and%20eight%20vacancies%20in%20the%20field%20of%20electrical%20engineering%2Felectrical%20and%20electronics%20engineering.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWho%20can%20apply%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20eligibility%20details%20for%20each%20role%20are%20as%20follows%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EScientist%2FEngineer%20(SC)%20(Polymer%20science%20and%20engineering%2Frubber%20technology)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Col%3E%20%3Cli%3EThe%20candidate%20should%20be%20between%2018%20and%2030%20years%20of%20age.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3ECandidates%20must%20possess%20an%20ME%2FMTech%20or%20an%20equivalent%20postgraduate%20degree%20in%20the%20discipline%20with%20a%20minimum%20aggregate%20of%2060%20percent%20or%20a%20CGPA%2FCPI%20grading%20of%206.5%20on%20a%2010-point%20scale.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3C%2Fol%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EScientist%2FEngineer%20(SC)%20(Electrical%20engineering%2Felectrical%20and%20electronics%20engineering)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Col%3E%20%3Cli%3EThe%20candidate%20should%20be%20between%2018%20and%2028%20years%20of%20age.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3ECandidates%20should%20have%20a%20BE%2FBTech%20or%20equivalent%20qualification%20in%20the%20discipline%20with%20a%20minimum%20aggregate%20of%2065%20percent%20marks%20or%20a%20CGPA%2FCPI%20grading%20of%206.84%20on%20a%2010-point%20scale.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3C%2Fol%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EScientist%2FEngineer%20(SC)%20(MSc%20agriculture%20%5Bhorticulture%2Fforestry%5D)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Col%3E%20%3Cli%3EThe%20candidate%20should%20be%20between%2018%20and%2028%20years%20of%20age.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3ECandidates%20must%20hold%20an%20MSc%20or%20an%20equivalent%20postgraduate%20degree%20in%20the%20field%20with%20a%20minimum%20aggregate%20of%2065%20percent%20marks%20or%20a%20CGPA%2FCPI%20grading%20of%206.84%20on%20a%2010-point%20scale.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3C%2Fol%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThings%20to%20know%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Col%3E%20%3Cli%3EThere%20will%20be%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F310225%2Ftech-tools-to-use-for-competitive-exam-preparation-iit-upsc-ias-officer-divya-mittal%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewritten%20test%20for%20candidates%3C%2Fa%3E%20based%20on%20their%20curriculum%20through%20offline%20mode%20in%20these%20cities%20%E2%80%94%20Guntur%2C%20Chennai%2C%20Bengaluru%20and%20Thiruvananthapuram.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EShortlisted%20candidates%20will%20then%20be%20called%20for%20an%20interview.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EAll%20selected%20candidates%20will%20receive%20a%20salary%20of%20Rs%2079%2C662%20per%20month%20along%20with%20HRA%20and%20transport%20allowance.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EUpon%20appointment%2C%20selected%20candidates%20will%20be%20under%20the%20purview%20of%20the%20National%20Pension%20System%20and%20will%20receive%20other%20benefits%20%E2%80%94%20including%20medical%20facilities%2C%20access%20to%20the%20canteen%20and%20library%2C%20leave%20travel%20concession%2C%20group%20insurance%2C%20etc%20%E2%80%94%20as%20applicable.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3C%2Fol%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20to%20apply%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Col%3E%20%3Cli%3EInterested%20candidates%20can%20apply%20online%20on%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.shar.gov.in%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C