%3E%20%3Cp%3EUntil%202020%2C%20only%20his%20patients%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F327134%2Fqueer-comedian-navin-noronha-on-navigating-comedy-circuit-in-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eappreciated%20his%20humour%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Today%2C%20however%2C%20thanks%20to%20social%20media%2C%20the%20entire%20world%20is%20laughing%20with%20him.%20In%20March%202020%2C%20his%20video%20on%20COVID-19%20went%20viral%2C%20giving%20rise%20to%20a%20genre%20he%20calls%20%E2%80%98Medcom%E2%80%99%20(medical%20comedy).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20positive%20response%20to%20his%20initial%20video%20led%20the%20doctor%20to%20create%20many%20videos%2C%20which%20focus%20on%20important%20medical%20topics%2C%20infused%20with%20humour%20to%20make%20them%20more%20palatable.%20Today%2C%20he%20has%20around%20two%20million%20subscribers%20across%20YouTube%20and%20Instagram.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPeople%20come%20to%20a%20gastroenterologist%20with%20diseases%20like%20haemorrhoids%20and%20piles%2C%20which%20they%20find%20embarrassing%20to%20describe.%20When%20patients%20have%20to%20discuss%20stool%20habits%2C%20related%20changes%2C%20acidity%20etc%2C%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20open%20up%20right%20away.%20So%20I%20started%20breaking%20the%20ice%20using%20a%20joke.%20They%20loved%20it%2C%20so%20I%20stuck%20to%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dr%20Pal%2C%20as%20he%20is%20fondly%20called%2C%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20appreciation%20for%20the%20doctor%E2%80%99s%20humour%20boosted%20his%20morale%20and%20opened%20up%20doors%20for%20him%20at%20a%20standup%20comedy%20club%20in%20Bay%20Area%2C%20California%2C%20called%20%E2%80%98Building%2018%E2%80%99.%20This%20kicked%20off%20the%2039-year-old%E2%80%99s%20stint%20as%20a%20comedian.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20joined%20Building%2018%20in%20May%202020%20and%20learnt%20tips%20and%20tricks%20on%20how%20to%20write%20a%20script%2C%20how%20to%20deliver%20a%20punch%2C%20what%20is%20stand-up%20comedy%20and%20much%20more.%20I%20found%20this%20to%20be%20much%20more%20difficult%20than%20medicine%2C%E2%80%9D%20laughs%20the%20doctor.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20his%20first%20standup%20show%20at%20the%20club%2C%20Dr%20Pal%20describes%20the%20experience%20as%20%E2%80%9Cincomparable%E2%80%9D.%20He%20says%20he%20spent%20hours%20preparing%20for%20his%2010-minute%20set%2C%20where%20he%20spoke%20about%20many%20serious%20medical%20issues%20in%20a%20comical%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWanting%20to%20grab%20this%20chance%20that%20life%20had%20given%20him%2C%20the%20doctor%20dove%20head%20first%20into%20comedy%2C%20creating%20reels%20and%20videos%2C%20and%20doing%20shows.%20Today%2C%20he%20does%20his%20%E2%80%98medcom%E2%80%99%20stand-up%20comedy%20shows%20in%20the%20US%2C%20India%2C%20Malaysia%20and%20Singapore.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20punchline%20for%20a%20health%20tip%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed%20wp-block-embed-youtube%20wp-embed-aspect-16-9%20wp-has-aspect-ratio%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed__wrapper%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%20data-origheight%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20data-epautoplay%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20data-facadesrc%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2F5_1yhDaDZfA%3Fenablejsapi%3D1%26amp%3Bautoplay%3D0%26amp%3Bcc_load_policy%3D0%26amp%3Biv_load_policy%3D3%26amp%3Bloop%3D0%26amp%3Bmodestbranding%3D0%26amp%3Bfs%3D1%26amp%3Bplaysinline%3D1%26amp%3Bcontrols%3D1%26amp%3Bcolor%3Dred%26amp%3Bcc_lang_pref%3D%26amp%3Brel%3D0%26amp%3Bautohide%3D2%26amp%3Btheme%3Ddark%26amp%3B%5C%22%20data-origwidth%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20data-spai-excluded%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2F5_1yhDaDZfA%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22YouTube%20player%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20Dr%20Pal%20started%20his%20YouTube%20journey%20with%20a%20video%20about%20COVID%2C%20what%20really%20catapulted%20him%20to%20fame%20was%20his%20video%20on%20intermittent%20fasting%2C%20where%20he%20shared%20his%20own%20weight%20loss%20journey.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20all%20started%20when%20the%20doctor%20had%20a%20health%20scare%20which%20made%20him%20sit%20up%20and%20take%20notice.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20100%20kg%20then%20and%20had%20palpitations%20while%20working.%20I%20realised%20how%20hypocritical%20I%20was%3B%20not%20practising%20what%20I%20was%20preaching.%20I%20had%20been%20studying%20medicine%20for%20almost%2015%20years%20but%20had%20forgotten%20to%20take%20care%20of%20my%20health%20in%20the%20process.%20I%20tried%20every%20diet%20but%20nothing%20worked%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20he%20started%20a%20research%20programme%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F327558%2Frevant-himatsingka-foodpharmer-shares-how-to-read-food-labels-for-health-risks%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eintermittent%20fasting%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20a%20few%20of%20his%20patients%20who%20had%20fatty%20liver.%20As%20the%20programme%20progressed%2C%20the%20doctor%20also%20started%20practising%20the%20same%20in%20his%20personal%20life.%20After%20losing%20almost%2025%20kg%2C%20he%20wanted%20to%20share%20the%20lessons%20he%20learned%20with%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20a%20doctor%2C%20I%20had%20such%20a%20tough%20time%20losing%20weight.%20I%20wondered%20how%20tough%20it%20is%20for%20non-medical%20people.%20That%E2%80%99s%20why%20I%20started%20making%20reels%20on%20Instagram%20to%20help%20people%20learn%20healthy%20habits%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDr%20Pal%20delivers%20these%20important%20messages%20%E2%80%94%20about%20gut%20health%2C%20fatty%20liver%2C%20heart%20health%2C%20foods%20to%20consume%2C%20and%20tips%20for%20a%20healthy%20lifestyle%20%E2%80%94%20with%20a%20comic%20element.%20To%20help%20deliver%20the%20message%20better%2C%20he%20created%20some%20imaginary%20characters%20like%20%E2%80%98Saravana%20Kumar%E2%80%99%20who%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20like%20following%20a%20diet.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Eat%20between%20sunrise%20and%20sunset%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCt1TuJ3LM_r%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCt1TuJ3LM_r%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCt1TuJ3LM_r%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20Dr.%20Pal%20Manickam%20(%40dr.pal.manickam)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Madurai-born%20doctor%20has%20advanced%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F332088%2Fmugdha-pradhan-ithrive-functional-medicine-mental-health-physical-health%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20training%20in%20nutrition%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20helps%20him%20preach%20better%20choices.%20Whereas%2C%20his%20humour%20gene%2C%20he%20says%20he%20inherited%20that%20from%20his%20father!%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDr%20Pal%20shares%20that%20his%20goal%20is%20to%20help%20people%20get%20healthier%20and%20decrease%20his%20business%20by%2030%20percent%20by%202030.%20%E2%80%9CI%20can%20guarantee%20that%20anybody%20who%20follows%20my%20channel%20religiously%20and%20follows%20what%20I%E2%80%99m%20promoting%20will%20definitely%20get%20healthier%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20want%20people%20to%20go%20back%20to%20the%20lifestyle%20our%20forefathers%20were%20following%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%20For%20instance%2C%20he%20suggests%20waking%20up%20early%20to%20watch%20the%20sunrise%20and%20eating%20the%20last%20meal%20before%20sunset.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EElaborating%20on%20how%20our%20ancestors%20lived%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThey%20never%20sat%20in%20a%20single%20place.%20They%20would%20go%20out%20hunting%20for%20food%20as%20soon%20as%20the%20sun%20rose%2C%20and%20ate%20wild%20berries%2C%20tubers%20and%20fibrous%20fruits.%C2%A0%20After%20walking%20around%20the%20entire%20day%2C%20they%20would%20cook%20whatever%20they%20collected%20before%20sunset%20and%20slept%20peacefully%20due%20to%20the%20production%20of%20melatonin%2C%20which%20helps%20sleep%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOne%20must%20think%20how%20much%20of%20this%20is%20being%20followed%20by%20our%20generation%20today.%20The%20doctor%20jokes%20that%20his%20friend%20Saravana%20Kumar%20wakes%20up%20before%20sunrise%20only%20to%20watch%20his%20favourite%20hero%E2%80%99s%20first-day-first-show%20movie%20in%20the%20theatre.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20sleeping%20two%20hours%20before%20sunrise%20these%20days!%20All%20the%20phones%20before%20bed%20neutralise%20the%20effects%20of%20melatonin%20and%20don%E2%80%99t%20let%20you%20sleep.%20We%20are%20also%20doing%20desk%20jobs%20without%20any%20movement.%20Try%20working%20and%20eating%20only%20between%20sunrise%20and%20sunset.%20This%20will%20help%20the%20circadian%20rhythm%20of%20the%20body.%20Have%20a%20winding%20routine%20post%20sunset%20and%20give%20rest%20to%20your%20body%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20advises.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDr%20Pal%20further%20urges%20everyone%20to%20lead%20a%20balanced%20life%20and%20not%20compromise%20on%20health.%20%E2%80%9CDon%E2%80%99t%20make%20this%20too%20complicated.%20You%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20to%20eat%20quinoa%20or%20expensive%20organic%20food.%20Just%20follow%20your%20ancestors%20and%20keep%20it%20simple%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%202123px)%20100vw%2C%202123px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FDSC07729_11zon-1698070642-scaled.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%222123%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dr%20Pal%20imparts%20crucial%20medical%20information%20through%20his%20stand-up%20comedy%20shows%20worldwide.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FDSC07729_11zon-1698070642-scaled.jpg%202123w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FDSC07729_11zon-1698070642-249x300.jpg%20249w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FDSC07729_11zon-1698070642-500x603.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FDSC07729_11zon-1698070642-768x926.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FDSC07729_11zon-1698070642-1274x1536.jpg%201274w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FDSC07729_11zon-1698070642-1698x2048.jpg%201698w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FDSC07729_11zon-1698070642-150x181.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-332866%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222560%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EDr%20Pal%20imparts%20crucial%20medical%20information%20through%20his%20stand-up%20comedy%20shows%20worldwide.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3ER%20Suguna%2C%20who%20follows%20Dr%20Pal%20on%20YouTube%2C%20says%20that%20she%20has%20become%20healthier%20after%20following%20his%20videos.%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20PCOS%20and%20was%20having%20a%20hard%20time%20losing%20weight.%20I%20also%20wanted%20to%20get%20my%20periods%20regularly.%20I%20started%20following%20intermittent%20fasting%20and%20moving%20throughout%20the%20day%20after%20watching%20Dr%20Pal%E2%80%99s%20videos.%20The%20change%20has%20been%20immense.%20Over%20the%20past%2014%20months%2C%20I%E2%80%99ve%20been%20able%20to%20regularise%20my%20periods%20and%20have%20much%20better%20stamina%20and%20energy%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Suguna.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDr%20Pal%20shares%20that%20his%20idea%20is%20to%20give%20tips%20and%20tricks%20in%20an%20interactive%2C%20interesting%20way%2C%20without%20making%20it%20feel%20like%20a%20lecture.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20love%20the%20satisfaction%20that%20comes%20from%20making%20people%20laugh.%20So%20many%20come%20up%20to%20me%20and%20share%20the%20changes%20in%20their%20lives%20after%20following%20my%20tips.%20They%20have%20tears%20in%20their%20eyes%20as%20they%20share%20their%20stories.%20It%20just%20leaves%20me%20awestruck.%20I%20just%20want%20people%20to%20get%20healthier%20and%20receive%20fewer%20patients%20at%20the%20hospital%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20his%20work%20in%20weight%20loss%2C%20a%20particular%20incident%20deeply%20touched%20the%20gastroenterologist.%20In%20one%20of%20his%20initial%20videos%2C%20he%20addressed%20the%20safety%20of%20COVID-19%20vaccines%2C%20prompting%20an%20elderly%20woman%20from%20Madurai%20to%20receive%20the%20vaccine.%20%E2%80%9CI%20received%20a%20letter%20from%20a%20woman%20in%20Thootukudi.%20She%20had%20lost%20her%20father%20to%20COVID%20as%20the%20vaccine%20was%20not%20av