treated%20like%20board%20exams.%20Only%20a%20few%20get%20selected.%20But%20what%20happens%20to%20the%20other%20children%3F%20Do%20we%20speak%20to%20them%20about%20what%20else%20they%20can%20do%3F%20Do%20we%20tell%20them%20it%E2%80%99s%20okay%20to%20fail%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F54484%2Fstudent-suicide-iit-jee-kota%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estudents%20at%20Kota%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20all%20school%20toppers%2C%20some%20of%20the%20brightest%20young%20minds%20of%20the%20country.%20They%20are%20not%20used%20to%20failure.%20The%20coaching%20system%20here%20divides%20them%20into%20ranks%20and%20offers%20handsome%20rewards%20to%20the%20toppers.%20They%20use%20children%20as%20a%20commodity%20and%20their%20parents%20put%20all%20their%20hopes%20and%20pressures%20on%20their%20children.%20But%2C%20what%20can%20a%20child%20do%20in%20this%3F%E2%80%9D%20asks%20Thakur.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWithout%20having%20a%20capacity%20or%20the%20facility%20to%20handle%20stress%2C%20children%20get%20flustered.%20Even%20adults%20struggle%20with%20managing%20stress%2C%20how%20will%20the%20young%20kids%20fare%20then%3F%20Everyone%20is%20a%20competitor%20and%20the%20parents%20go%20to%20great%20lengths%20to%20send%20their%20wards%20to%20Kota%2C%20where%20the%20coaching%20institutes%20have%20very%20high%20fees.%20Different%20reports%20suggest%20that%20the%20Kota%20coaching%20market%20generates%20more%20than%20Rs%206%2C000%20crores%20per%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERavi%20(name%20changed)%20came%20to%20Kota%20in%20June%202023.%20The%2016-year-old%E2%80%99s%20family%20owns%20a%20small%20grocery%20store%20in%20Kanpur%20and%20his%20father%20wanted%20him%20to%20become%20an%20engineer%20as%20he%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20become%20one.%20He%20was%20raised%20with%20the%20expectations%20of%20studying%20in%20an%20IIT%20and%20being%20the%20harbinger%20of%20hope%20for%20his%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%2