f%20mental%20health.%20%E2%80%9CBrain%20is%20also%20a%20part%20of%20the%20body.%20Parents%20have%20to%20understand%20this%20fact%20and%20give%20issues%20of%20the%20mind%20that%20much%20importance.%20Parents%20keep%20telling%20their%20children%20about%20the%20sacrifices%20they%E2%80%99ve%20made%20and%20the%20financial%20burden%20to%20send%20them%20to%20Kota%2C%20adding%20to%20a%20teenager%E2%80%99s%20woes%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAside%20from%20parents%2C%20the%20major%20issue%20is%20with%20the%20education%20system.%20These%20stakeholders%20say%20that%20the%20government%20must%20work%20on%20modifying%20the%20format%20of%20competitive%20exams%2C%20making%20it%20less%20rejective.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20students%2C%20they%20must%20have%20a%20Plan%20B%2C%20urges%20Thakur.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAll%20of%20us%20can%E2%80%99t%20become%20doctors%20and%20engineers.%20Some%20of%20us%20will%20be%20successful%2C%20some%20not.%20Keep%20a%20Plan%20B%20ready.%20It%E2%80%99s%20better%20than%20Plan%20A%20in%20most%20cases.%20You%E2%80%99ll%20flourish%2C%20don%E2%80%99t%20worry.%20Becoming%20a%20doctor%20or%20engineer%20is%20the%20means%20to%20the%20goal%3B%20it%20can%E2%80%99t%20be%20the%20goal%20itself.%20So%20make%20friends%2C%20have%20some%20hobbies%20and%20enjoy%20your%20student%20life%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Thakur.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EVijayvargiya%20says%20students%20must%20learn%20that%20failures%20are%20common.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20to%20accept%20that%20competition%20is%20inevitable.%20Teach%20your%20children%20that%20it%E2%80%99s%20okay%20to%20fail.%20Put%20in%20your%20best%2C%20work%20hard%2C%20but%20don%E2%80%99t%20lose%20heart%20if%20you%20don%E2%80%99t%20get%20what%20you%20want%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMany%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F331067%2Framji-swaminathan-craftizan-miniature-models-of-isro-rockets-sate